03e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eDrawing inspiration from the vast network of existing machinery within the museum, Onyx was originally conceived as a meditation on the duality of human and robot, past and present.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-coffee-bar-custom-terrazzo-tiles-110225-1049-04.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-coffee-bar-custom-terrazzo-tiles-110225-1049-04.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-coffee-bar-custom-terrazzo-tiles-110225-1049-04-940x752.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-coffee-bar-custom-terrazzo-tiles-110225-1049-04-800x640.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-coffee-bar-custom-terrazzo-tiles-110225-1049-04-768x614.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-coffee-bar-custom-terrazzo-tiles-110225-1049-04-1536x1229.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn contrast to the raw materials of the museum, the cafe is carefully curated. Shades of pink set the space apart from the rest of the museum, immersing guests in an experience. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-coffee-bar-custom-terrazzo-tiles-110225-1049-05.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-coffee-bar-custom-terrazzo-tiles-110225-1049-05.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-coffee-bar-custom-terrazzo-tiles-110225-1049-05-940x1175.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/modern-coffee-bar-custom-terrazzo-tiles-11